107.name: Disrespect
107.desc: Damage +9% to foes with 30% or lower HP.

110.name: Ether Predator
110.desc: Attacking a foe creates an Ether that only you can collect. On collecting the Ether, Atk. Power +0.2% for 90s and All Defense +0.3%. Stacks up to 30 times. Chance on Ether collection to increases the stack by 3. (Cooldown: 10s)

111.name: Stabilized Status
111.desc: Damage +3% when your HP is above 80%.

118.name: Grudge
118.desc: Damage +4% to Boss or above monsters. Incoming Damage +20%.

119.name: Invincible Evasion
119.desc: Become invincible while using your Movement Skill.

125.name: Mayhem
125.desc: Fury Meter remains at max, and turns into Burst Mode with the power of darkness. Burst Mode: Outgoing Damage +3%, Atk. and Move Speed +15%, all incoming Damage -65%. When Burst Mode activates, HP is reduced to 25% of Max HP; this cannot be exceeded even when Healing is applied. Can only receive 40% of healing effects and 25% of shield. Press the [X] key to cancel Burst Mode and recover 25% of Max HP, but cannot enter Burst Mode again for 30s.

127.name: Esoteric Skill Enhancement
127.desc: Max number of Esoteric Orbs +1. Esoteric skills inflict +8% Damage per Esoteric Orb you have.

129.name: Enhanced Weapon
129.desc: Changing Stances enhances your weapon. Crit Rate +20% for 9s.

130.name: Firepower Enhancement
130.desc: When the Firepower Meter is full, Overheat effect is triggered. Normal Skill Damage +4% and Firepower Meter duration +8s. When not in Barrage Mode, Incoming Damage -5%.

133.name: Balanced Defense
133.desc: Phy. or Mag. Defense value increased to match whichever is highest.

134.name: Drops of Ether
134.desc: Attacks have a chance to create an Ether within 8 meters. (Cooldown: 60s)

140.name: Crisis Evasion
140.desc: When receiving fatal Damage, become invincible for 3s, recovering 50% of the Damage taken during invincibility as HP. (Cooldown: 15m)

141.name: Keen Blunt Weapon
141.desc: +10% Crit Damage but your attacks have a chance to deal -20% Damage.

168.name: MP Efficiency Increase
168.desc: MP Recovery +5%. When MP is at 50% or below, Damage to foes +3%.

188.name: Berserker's Technique
188.desc: During Burst, Outgoing Damage +16%. After Burst, Exhaustion does not occur.

189.name: First Intention
189.desc: Damage to foes +16%, but you can no longer gain Esoteric Meter.

190.name: Ultimate Skill: Taijutsu
190.desc: Natural recovery speed of Stamina Energy +300%. Stamina skill Damage +35%. Shock Skill Damage -30%.

191.name: Shock Training
191.desc: Shock Skill Damage +10%. 2% of max Shock Energy recovered every 1s.

192.name: Pistoleer
192.desc: Can only use the Handgun Stance. Handgun Skill Damage +30%. Stagger Damage +40%. Awakening Skill Damage +15%.

193.name: Barrage Enhancement
193.desc: Barrage Skill Damage +5%. Barrage Skill Crit Rate +20%. Barrage Meter Gain +30%. Does not enter in cooling state.

194.name: True Courage
194.desc: Your outgoing Damage from Serenade of Courage +10% and Crit Rate +10%.

195.name: Desperate Salvation
195.desc: When the recovery effect ends, an additional recovery effect is activated, recovering 8% of your Max HP.

196.name: Rage Hammer
196.desc: When using a Gravity Release Skill, Crit Rate +3% and Crit Damage +5% based on the amount of Cores used.

197.name: Gravity Training
197.desc: Gravity Meter +20% upon using Gravity Release Skill. In Hypergravity Mode, Crit Rate of basic attacks and Vortex Gravity +10%. Outgoing Damage +4%. When the Hypergravity Skill hits the same foe 3 times, cause a "Gravity Shock" which inflicts additional Damage. Damage inflicted by Gravity Shock is influenced by Hypergravity Skill Damage.

198.name: Master Summoner
198.desc: Enhances the Ancient Elemental Skill. Elemental Orb cost -1. Normal Skill Damage and Ancient Elemental Skill Damage +2% and Crit Rate +3%.

199.name: Communication Overflow
199.desc: Summon duration +5% for Maririn, Pauru, Elcid, Shurdi, and Kelsion. Damage +10%. Atk. Speed and Move Speed +3%. Command Skill Cooldown -3%.

200.name: Empress's Grace
200.desc: 4-stack Ruin Damage +20%. When Ruin hits, recover 30% of consumed MP.

201.name: Order of the Emperor
201.desc: Adds Emperor Cards to the Card Deck. Balance and Judgment Cards are replaced with Chancellor and Empress Cards. Normal Skill Damage +20%.

203.name: Vagabond
203.desc: Atk. Power +4% when not in a Party or Raid.

206.name: Telescope
206.desc: Guardians' whereabouts are always displayed on the map. This effect is applied to all of your party members.

224.name: Combat Readiness
224.desc: Normal skills Damage +20%. Shield Amount +30% in Defensive Stance. Damage +4% for 10s when hit while in Defensive Stance (stacked up to 3 times, once every 1s).

225.name: Lone Knight
225.desc: Gunlance skill Crit Rate +5%. Crit Damage +30%. Battlefield Shield cannot be used. Shield Meter consumption during Defensive Stance +100%.

235.name: Fortitude
235.desc: Incoming Damage is reduced proportional to HP lost. (Max. 5%)

236.name: Crushing Fist
236.desc: On successful Counter Attack, Atk. Power +4%. For 3s Countered target takes +2% Damage from all party members.

238.name: Master's Tenacity
238.desc: Outgoing Damage +3% at 50% or lower HP.

239.name: Divine Protection
239.desc: When attacked, there is a 20% chance of activing Divine Protection which reduces the Damage received by 60%. (Cooldown: 60s)

240.name: Heavy Armor
240.desc: All Defense +20%. This additional Defense is immune to Defense Reduction effects.

242.name: Enhanced Shield
242.desc: Become immune to all Status Ailments while affected by shields, but -90% Shields' HP and Defensive Stance's Damage absorption amounts. (Not applicable to Battlefield Shield)

243.name: Necromancy
243.desc: Attacks summon temporary soldiers that Damage foes. (Cooldown: 75s)

244.name: Preemptive Strike
244.desc: When attacking Challenge or lower monsters with full HP, your attack is a guaranteed crit with +30% Damage.

246.name: Lightning Fury
246.desc: Attacks have a 60% chance of generating a lightning orb. These lightning orbs can only be generated once every 4s. When 5 orbs are created, they explode and Damage surrounding foes.

247.name: Cursed Doll
247.desc: Atk. Power +3%. Healing -25%, natural recovery excluded.

248.name: Contender
248.desc: Atk. Power +1% for 15s after killing a foe. (Max. 5 stacks)

250.name: Ether Blast
250.desc: When obtained, Ethers deal Mag. Damage equal to 50% of your Max HP.

251.name: Magick Stream
251.desc: Stacks up to +5% MP Recovery every 3s while you are not attacked. When the maximum stack is reached, skill Cooldown -3%. Being hit removes 1 stack of the effect with a Cooldown of 10s.

252.name: Double Jump
252.desc: 10% chance when using a Movement Skill to reset its Cooldown.

254.name: Raid Captain
254.desc: Outgoing Damage +10% of basic Move Speed bonus percentage.

256.name: Energy Overflow
256.desc: Energy does not go below 1, but additional Energy Recovery effect is not applied during Hype. If Energy is below 30%, Damage to foes +5%.

257.name: Robust Spirit
257.desc: When using Hype, enters level 3 immediately. While in Hype Mode, Energy recovery speed +200%. Damage +10%.

258.name: Loyal Companion
258.desc: Summons Silverhawk MK-II, allowing Move Speed +4%, Silverhawk's Basic AoE Radius +60%, Silverhawk's Basic Attack Damage +100%, and Silverhawk's summon duration +30%. On Basic Attack or Wings of Storm hit, foes get a Mark of Death: foe Damage taken +4%. Additionally, when Silverhawk is summoned Atk. Power +3%.

259.name: Death Strike
259.desc: When using Last Rush, recover 50% of the remaining Hawk Meter. Damage taken +22% for 8s.

114.name: Twinkle Twinkle
114.desc: 10% chance of obtaining an additional Ability Stone.

207.name: Dynamite
207.desc: Obtain materials once more per ore vein when using Mining Bomb.

211.name: Master Net Caster
211.desc: Net Casting is always available, but it costs 5 Fishing Tools.

213.name: Giant Tree
213.desc: Cut down trees of a rank higher than your current logging level.

214.name: Sapling
214.desc: 3% chance of a sapling sprouting up where you logged.

215.name: 4-Leaf Clover
215.desc: 2% chance while foraging to gather twice the amount.

217.name: Entomologist
217.desc: 2% chance to discover a larva after foraging.

219.name: Butcher
219.desc: 4% chance that your allotted skill uses won't decrease while carving.

221.name: Delicate Brush
221.desc: Excavation minigames are easier, with a +30% chance of extra loot.

264.name: Double Points
264.desc: 15% chance to get extra items while Mystery Point Fishing.

265.name: Golden Bait
265.desc: Throw Bait uses higher quality bait, increasing the duration of This Is The Big One to 110s.

267.name: Rapid Kick
267.desc: 50% chance to reset Cooldown of Kick Tree is used.

269.name: Deceptive Foraging
269.desc: 8% chance that your allotted skill uses won't decrease while foraging.

271.name: Deadly Poison
271.desc: Machete hits paralyzes huge prey, regardless of the rank of the machete you have equipped.

272.name: Golden Rabbit
272.desc: Chance for a Golden Rabbit +4% when using Search or Prey Searching.

274.name: Loot Hunter
274.desc: 4% chance upon digging to discover an additional treasure chest.

276.name: Pinnacle
276.desc:
Adds Pinnacle: Flurry/Focus I instead of the Flurry/Focus Stage 3 effect added upon changing stances while the Dual Meter is maxed at Level 3.
Pinnacle: Flurry I: Atk. Speed + 12.5%, Damage +12.5%, Crit Rate +20%
Pinnacle: Focus I: Move Speed +15%, Damage +15%, Crit Damage +37.5%

277.name: Control
277.desc: Cannot use Focus stance. Flurry skills Damage +18%.

278.name: Remaining Energy
278.desc: Death Trance does not consume Death Orb Meter for 2s when activated. Atk./Move Speed +6% and Atk. Power +(8%, 16%, 25%) depending on the number of Death Orbs available when using Deathblade Surge, for 30s.

279.name: Surge Zero
279.desc: Deathblade Surge changes to Surge Zero, which unleashes the same powerful attack regardless of the number of Death Orbs available. With Surge Zero, the buffs from the Remaining Energy Engraving do not occur. When Death Trance is activated and skills other than Basic Attacks and Awakening Skills hit, Surge Enhancement effects will begin to stack every 0.4 seconds to a max of 20 stacks. This effect causes Surge Zero Damage to increase up to 100%, Damage increases even more with larger stacks. When Death Trance ends, gain up to 100% Death Orb Meter for each Surge Enhancement effect you have.

280.name: Perfect Suppression
280.desc: Normal Skill Damage +20%. Shadowburst Meter +50% for all skills. Disables Demonize.

281.name: Demonic Impulse
281.desc: The Composure effect does not activate when Demonize ends. Upon Demonize, Demonic Skill Cooldown is reset.

282.name: Judgment
282.desc: Punishment Damage +15%. When Punishment skill hits, Piety Meter gain +100%. Duration of Sacred Executioner +100%.

283.name: Blessed Aura
283.desc: With Holy Aura, Damage received -10% and 2% of Max HP restored every 2.5s for all party members.

284.name: Arthetinean Skill
284.desc: Increases damage of Drone and Joint skills by 15%, and increases Battery Max by 10%. Increase Move Speed by 10% when a Drone is attached to a Machinist.

285.name: Evolutionary Legacy
285.desc: During Hypersync Mode, on hit, Sync skills inflict Damage +2% (Max. 3 stacks) and Cooldown -0.5s. Also, Hypersync Mode returns 40% of its Core Energy cost when canceled.

286.name: Hunger
286.desc: Chaos Meter +30%. Atk. Power +12% when the Chaos Meter is full.

287.name: Lunar Voice
287.desc: Swoop Damage +120% instead of the Swoop Enhancement effect that stacks every 1s upon switching to Persona Mode.

289.name: Peacemaker
289.desc: Atk. Speed +8% in Handgun Stance. Crit Rate +10% and Outgoing Damage +5% in Shotgun Stance. Outgoing Damage +10% and additional Damage +10% for 9s to targets with 50% or lower HP while in Rifle Stance.

290.name: Time to Hunt
290.desc: Handgun and Rifle Skills' Crit Rate +22%. Unable to use Shotgun Stance.

291.name: Deathblow
291.desc: Max number of Esoteric Orbs +1. Esoteric skills consume all Esoteric Orbs and inflict +17% Damage per Esoteric Orb consumed.

292.name: Esoteric Flurry
292.desc: Only 1 Esoteric Orb is used when using Esoteric Skill, and Esoteric Skill Damage +8%.

293.name: Igniter
293.desc: When Magick Amplification is triggered, normal skills' Cooldown -50%. During Magick Amplification, Crit Rate +10% and Crit Damage +20%.

294.name: Reflux
294.desc: Disables Arcane Rupture, but Damage of skills (except Awakening and Movement skills) +8% and Cooldown -3%.

296.name: Propulsion
296.desc: After using a Movement Skill, Damage of skills (excluding Basic Attack and Awakening Skills) +3% for 5s.

297.name: Hit Master
297.desc: Damage of attacks other than Back Attack and Frontal Attack +3%. Does not apply to Awakening Skills.

298.name: Sight Focus
298.desc: When "!!!!!" is entered into normal chat, Sight Focus is activated for 6s. After the effect is activated, offensive skill Damage +8%. Only half of the effect is applied to Awakening Skills. Does not apply to Basic Attack. Cooldown: 30s.

299.name: Adrenaline
299.desc: After using skills (excluding Movement Skills and Basic Attacks), Atk. Power +0.3% for 6s. Stacks up to 6 times. When max stacks are reached, Crit Rate +5%. If Cooldown reduction due to skill cancel is applied to this effect, it is applied after the end of the skill.

300.name: All-Out Attack
300.desc: Holding and Casting skill Speed +5%. Damage +4%.

301.name: Expert
301.desc: Shield and Healing effectiveness on all Party Members +6%. If target's HP is 50% or lower, +3% additional effectiveness.

302.name: Emergency Rescue
302.desc: When HP falls below 30%, gain a shield equal to 20% of Max HP for 6s. If the shield is not destroyed after 6s, recover 50% of the remaining shield as HP. (Cooldown: 300s.)

305.name: Recurrence
305.desc: Upon using Moonfall or Sunrise, gain an effect that increases the Artist's Crit Rate by <$CALC <$MACRO buffstat0_100 @1:500194/>/>% and Crit Damage by <$CALC <$MACRO buffstat1_100 @1:500194/>/>% for 60s.

306.name: Full Bloom
306.desc: When casting Sunrise, the energy spreads to recover HP of Party Members within 24m of the Artist and Sun Marble. It recovers up to <$CALC (<$TABLE_SKILLEFFECT ValueD 311114/>/100)/>% of the Artist's max HP.

307.name: Nothing Can Stop Me
307.desc: Crit Rate +7% of the basic Move Speed Bonus percentage, and Crit damage +22% of the basic Atk. Speed Increase percentage. If Umbrella skill is used and then again within 3s, recover max 12% of Raindrop Meter. Sun Shower is enhanced and counts as an Umbrella skill. Sun Shower AoE radius is reduced and Raindrop Meter consumption +50%. Foes no longer receive the Atk. Power Reduction effect, but Atk. Speed and Move Speed Increase of allies +12%.

308.name: Drizzle
308.desc: Sun Shower's Raindrop Meter consumption decreases by 50%. While Sun Shower is active, damage dealt by Weather skills increases by 7%.

77300001.name: Expert
77300001.desc: Shield and Healing effectiveness on all Party Members +6%. If target's HP is 50% or lower, +3% additional effectiveness.

77300002.name: Emergency Rescue
77300002.desc: When HP falls below 30%, gain a shield equal to 20% of Max HP for 6s. If the shield is not destroyed after 6s, recover 50% of the remaining shield as HP. (Cooldown: 300s.)
